  "texts": [
    "https://stackoverflow.com/help/gpt-policy If the main objective is to imitate human language generation, then creating such a tool is futile!",
    "In other words, if such a tool functions well, then perhaps ChatGPT is not human-like enough in its language processing.",
    "Unless, of course, OpenAI is trying to incorporate distinctive markers (i.e.",
    "watermarks[30]) in the generated text!",
    "Tasks such as this can be used to assess the intelligence of language models."
  ]
}